  "details": "A security vulnerability has been detected in zyx0814 FilePress up to 2.2.0. Affected by this vulnerability is an unknown functionality of the file dzz/shares/admin.php of the component Shares Filelist API. Such manipulation of the argument order leads to sql injection. The attack can be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed publicly and may be used. The name of the patch is e20ec58414103f781858f2951d178e19b1736664. A patch should be applied to remediate this issue.",
